{"text_id":214821,"tokens":["Mari","juana"," legalization"," in"," three"," states"," -"," Arizona",","," Montana",","," and"," New"," Jersey"," -"," was"," not"," so"," much"," a"," sudden"," change"," as"," it"," was"," the"," culmination"," of"," a"," long","-","standing"," movement","."," This"," movement"," has"," gained"," momentum"," over"," the"," past"," few"," years",","," with"," an"," increasing"," number"," of"," states"," legal","izing"," marijuana"," for"," medical"," or"," recreational"," use","."," Here"," are"," some"," key"," factors"," that"," contributed"," to"," this"," recent"," wave"," of"," legalization",":","\n\n","1","."," Shifting"," public"," opinion",":"," According"," to"," polls"," conducted"," by"," Gallup"," and"," Pew"," Research"," Center",","," a"," majority"," of"," Americans"," now"," support"," marijuana"," legalization","."," This"," shift"," in"," public"," opinion"," has"," put"," pressure"," on"," state"," governments"," to"," change"," their"," marijuana"," laws",".","\n\n","2","."," Revenue"," generation",":"," With"," state"," budgets"," strained"," due"," to"," the"," COVID","-","1","9"," pandemic",","," many"," states"," are"," looking"," for"," new"," sources"," of"," revenue","."," Legal","izing"," and"," taxing"," marijuana"," provides"," a"," way"," to"," generate"," revenue"," while"," also"," reducing"," law"," enforcement"," costs"," associated"," with"," prohibition",".","\n\n","3","."," Social"," justice",":"," There"," is"," a"," growing"," recognition"," that"," the"," war"," on"," drugs"," has"," disproportion","ately"," affected"," communities"," of"," color","."," Legal","izing"," marijuana"," is"," seen"," as"," a"," step"," towards"," addressing"," these"," racial"," disparities"," and"," reducing"," the"," number"," of"," people"," incarcerated"," for"," non","-","violent"," drug"," offenses",".","\n\n","4","."," Medical"," benefits",":"," There"," is"," a"," growing"," body"," of"," evidence"," highlighting"," the"," medical"," benefits"," of"," marijuana",","," particularly"," in"," the"," treatment"," of"," chronic"," pain",","," nausea",","," and"," seizures","."," Legal","izing"," marijuana"," for"," medical"," use"," allows"," patients"," to"," access"," these"," benefits"," without"," resorting"," to"," the"," illegal"," market",".","\n\n","5","."," Political"," will",":"," In"," some"," cases",","," legalization"," was"," driven"," by"," the"," political"," will"," of"," elected"," officials","."," In"," New"," Jersey",","," for"," example",","," Governor"," Phil"," Murphy"," campaigned"," on"," a"," platform"," that"," included"," marijuana"," legalization",".","\n\n","It"," is"," worth"," noting"," that"," marijuana"," remains"," illegal"," at"," the"," federal"," level","."," However",","," the"," recent"," wave"," of"," legalization"," at"," the"," state"," level"," is"," a"," significant"," development"," that"," reflects"," changing"," attitudes"," towards"," marijuana"," use","."," It"," is"," likely"," that"," we"," will"," see"," more"," states"," follow"," suit"," in"," the"," coming"," years","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}